<h3 id="four-channel">Four Channel</h3>

<p>Those 4 channel meters in the list below are all basically identical. Just that the CENTER 304 (and one of the two VOLTCRAFT K204, no typo here!, does not include any data logging capability. However, that does not matter for its use with Artisan. Therefore, selecting the CENTER 304 over the CENTER309 makes sense as it is usually the cheaper device (so take care, there are two different devices labeled VOLTCRAFT K204, but they can easily be distinguished by price).</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="http://www.centertek.com/product_d.php?lang=en&amp;tb=1&amp;id=76&amp;cid=67">CENTER 304</a> / VOLTCRAFT K204
